<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="strcspn" id="strcspn">strcspn</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntaxe :
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">size_t</span> <span class="kw3">strcspn</span> <span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>str1, <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>str2<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

La fonction <code>strcspn()</code> renvoie la position du premier caractère de <code>str1</code>
qui correspond à l&#039;un des caractères de <code>str2</code>.
</p>

